The paper deals with an evaluation approach for functional logic computations, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL) and logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the correctness of the approach, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE). The pull-tabbing approach is a graph transformation, which can be categorized under formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
